OL,3,CMum whose daughter took own life joins
OL,4,Cyouth suicide campaign
OL,6,FA mother from Lincolnshire has shared
OL,7,Fthe story of her daughter's life in a
OL,8,Fnew video as part of a campaign aimed
OL,9,Fat preventing suicide among young
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,FFifteen-year-old Evelyn Gibson, from
OL,13,FGrantham, took her own life in 2022
OL,14,Fafter struggling with mental health
OL,15,Fissues.
OL,17,FHer mother and stepfather, Jenni and
OL,18,FJack Swift, have launched a campaign
OL,19,Fwith CALM (Campaign Against Living
OL,20,FMiserably) to raise awareness of
OL,21,Fsuicide in young people.
