OL,3,CMum whose daughter took own life joins
OL,4,Cyouth suicide campaign
OL,6,F"When Evelyn was unwell we didn't
OL,7,Freally know where to turn to for help
OL,8,Fand we found it really isolating,"
OL,9,FJenni said.
OL,11,F"We found it hard to talk to Evelyn
OL,12,Fabout what she was feeling. For us
OL,13,Ftaking on this campaign we wanted to
OL,14,Fcarry on a legacy for her and we want
OL,15,Fto prevent other families from going
OL,16,Fthrough what we're continuing to go
OL,17,Fthrough every day."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
