OL,3,CMum whose daughter took own life joins
OL,4,Cyouth suicide campaign
OL,6,FCALM has released the video 'Evelyn'
OL,7,Fas part of its Missed Birthdays
OL,8,Fcampaign, to highlight the birthdays
OL,9,Fyoung people miss after taking their
OL,10,Fown lives.
OL,12,FThe video features moments in Evelyn's
OL,13,Flife in the run-up to what would have
OL,14,Fbeen her 16th birthday.
OL,16,FJenni hopes the video will encourage
OL,17,Fparents to learn more about suicide
OL,18,Fand poor mental health.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
