OL,3,CMum whose daughter took own life joins
OL,4,Cyouth suicide campaign
OL,6,FShe said: "We talk to our young people
OL,7,Fabout sex and drugs and the risks
OL,8,Fassociated with those but we don't
OL,9,Ftalk to them about mental health and
OL,10,Fsuicide.
OL,12,F"As adults it is really important we
OL,13,Fhave the tools to know how to approach
OL,14,Fthose conversations.
OL,16,F"Parents shouldn't be afraid to have
OL,17,Fthat conversation with their children
OL,18,For be afraid to ask them 'Are you
OL,19,Ffeeling suicidal?'"
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
