OL,3,CMum whose daughter took own life joins
OL,4,Cyouth suicide campaign
OL,6,FIn the last 10 years, almost 7,000
OL,7,Fyoung people in the UK took their own
OL,8,Flives. Suicide is the most common
OL,9,Fcause of death for under 24-year-olds.
OL,11,FBut YouGov research, commissioned by
OL,12,FCALM, found 65% of UK adults wouldn't
OL,13,Ffeel confident about where to turn if
OL,14,Fthey needed to support a young person
OL,15,Fwith suicidal thoughts.
OL,17,FJack, said: "People think talking
OL,18,Fabout suicide gets the idea into a
OL,19,Fperson's head. Talking about suicide
OL,20,Fdoes not cause suicide. It might just
OL,21,Fsave them.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
