OL,3,CMum whose daughter took own life joins
OL,4,Cyouth suicide campaign
OL,6,F"Parents just need to be real and not
OL,7,Ftip-toe around the situation."
OL,9,FCALM spokesperson Elizabeth
OL,10,FCharlesworth said: "Youth suicide is
OL,11,Fclimbing at a rate faster than we have
OL,12,Fever seen before so it really needs to
OL,13,Fbe a priority to prevent any more
OL,14,Fdeaths.
OL,16,F"It was so important for us to use
OL,17,FEvelyn's story and to speak with Jenni
OL,18,Fand Jack as it removes the stigma
OL,19,Faround suicide."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
